# Developer rules for China Macro Observatory

# Blacklist Virtual Paths / In-memory directories from autocomplete & indexers
_pyrefly_virtual__/inmemory
_pyrefly_virtual__
.venv
__pycache__
*.db
*.xlsx

# Engineering standard guidelines
- Strict Python compilation check before commits (python -m py_compile App.py)
- Run ruff check on changes (ruff check .)
- Maintain exact 40-60 characters constraints for Sina Live News Feed summaries
- Do not modify existing UI styling colors
